How to install sp flash tool in kali linux 2018.2 :


1) sudo apt-get update [ command in terminal ]

2) sudo apt install libusb-dev [ command in terminal ]

3) sudo apt install libqtwebkit4  [ command in terminal ]



4) download latest sp flash tool zip file for linux from https://androidmtk.com/smart-phone-flash-tool 
extract the zip file

5) Get in the extract folder of sp flash tool..
open terminal...


6) chmod +x flash_tool [ command in terminal ]

7) ./flash_tool [ command in terminal ]

now done ...Happy flasing....
